name: A Gambler's Best Friend
description:
A Gambler's Best Friend

A limited edition print on white tone semi-gloss poster stock, hand-signed and numbered by the designer Paul Poppenburg. Will be shipped from the Netherlands in a reinforced mail tube within 1-3 days of order, please allow 1-2 weeks for delivery. Approximately 16” x 24” or 40x60 centimeters. Limited edition of 50 pieces worldwide!
